net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.common

Enum LengthProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LengthProperty>
      • net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.common.LengthProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<LengthProperty>, CssProperty, AttributeReadValue<String>, Datatype, SimpleDatatype<String>

    public enum LengthProperty
extends Enum<LengthProperty>
implements SimpleDatatype<String>, CssProperty
    This enum contains the available properties that are configured with Length values. Both value and string representation are the CSS property name.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
    See Also:
    Length
